      <div type="chapter" xml:id="p1">
        <head>Prathama Patra (Page 1)</head>

        <p>अथ <choice><sic>पाठ</sic><corr>पाठः</corr></choice> आरभ्यते।</p>

        <p>
          एषः <add place="interline">शुद्धः</add> श्लोकः अस्ति।
          <note place="left">Left margin note — commentary by later hand.</note>
        </p>

        <p>
          <del>दोषयुक्तः</del> पाठः इत्युक्तम्।
          <note place="right">Right margin note — editor's warning.</note>
        </p>

        <p>
          तत्र <note place="top">Top margin note: reference to another folio.</note>
          शुद्धलेखः दृश्यते।
        </p>

        <p>
          <note place="bottom">Bottom margin note: possible scribal insertion.</note>
          इत्यमरः।
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- PAGE 2 -->
      <pb n="2"/>
      <div type="chapter" xml:id="p2">
        <head>Dvitīya Patra (Page 2)</head>

        <p>
          अत्र <choice><sic>विद्य</sic><corr>विद्या</corr></choice> शब्दः प्रयुज्यते।
          <add>समीकृतम्।</add>
          <note place="top">Top note — gloss on विद्या.</note>
        </p>

        <p>
          सः श्लोकः <add>संपादितः</add> पुनः पठनीयः।
          <note place="left">Left note — duplicate version in another MS.</note>
        </p>

        <p>
          अस्य <del>विवादः</del> न कश्चन।
          <note place="bottom">Bottom note — marginal cross-reference.</note>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- PAGE 3 -->
      <pb n="3"/>
      <div type="chapter" xml:id="p3">
        <head>Tṛtīya Patra (Page 3)</head>

        <p>
          इदानीं समापनम्।
          <note place="right">Right margin note — end marker.</note>
          <note place="bottom">Bottom note — later addition.</note>
        </p>

        <p>
          <add>समाप्तिः।</add>
        </p>
